"step back in time to ancient Mesopotamia where the Sumerians pioneered a revolutionary concept that would change the course of humanity writing in the city of yurak a curious young boy named enki had an idea that would reshape how people communicate and record information with Clay tokens used for trade as his inspiration enki developed cuneiform script a system of wet-shaped marks etched onto clay tablets these tablets became the canvas for laws stories and records of daily life this Innovative approach spread rapidly influencing neighboring civilizations and leaving an indelible mark on history "